Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), build-essential
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/braemons/vstimd
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: vstimd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libvulkan1, adduser
Recommends: vulkan-tools
Description: Visual stimulus display server for neuroscience experiments
 vstimd drives a display directly via VK_KHR_display without a compositor,
 providing sub-millisecond frame timing for psychophysics experiments.
 .
 Communicates via ZMQ (port 5555) using a protobuf protocol. Supports
 Jetson Orin Nano, Raspberry Pi 4/5, and desktop NVIDIA GPUs.
